'''Teleq''' was one of six [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] hired by [[Granta Omega]] to capture [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] on a training mission to [[Ragoon VI]]. He captured the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Wren Honoran]], and intended to use him to capture the Jedi. His plan was foiled, however, after attempting to down the Jedi with waves of poison darts, and he was carried away by angry bird-like creatures when Obi-Wan and Anakin drove him into the birds' guarded nests where they protected their young.

Teleq was fond of traps and had a cunning way with technology.

